    "created_at": "2026-01-18T16:16:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-01-18T16:16:38Z",
    "body": "This is just one in a long succession of failures in `BlueprintCircuit`.  `QuantumCircuit` is generally _not_ subclass safe, and `BlueprintCircuit` tried not only to subclass it, but to change core functionality about the class too.  It's the reason it will be removed in 3.0.\n\nI'd like to keep any fixes isolated to `BlueprintCircuit` itself - I don't want the rest of Qiskit to be affected by it, especially since we've moved the circuit library away from it.",
