    "updated_at": "2026-01-19T16:58:34Z",
    "body": "What if we add `_circuit_data` property to `QuantumCircuit` and override it in `BlueprintCircuit` to trigger a self-build on demand, and then call `getattr(\"_circuit_data\")` in `FromPyObject` of `QuantumCircuitData`?",
